title: DBSK (TVXQ) - O.Jung.Ban.Hap (Japanese Edition)
description:
TVXQ's "O" - Jung.Ban.Hap album.  This is the Japanese Edition with the Japanese version of You're My Miracle.  

1. "O" Jung.Ban.Hap
2. You're My Miracle (Korean Version)
3. Hey! Girl
4. Get Me Some
5. I'll Be There
6. White Lie...
7. Remember
8. The Story Has Just Begun
9. On & On
10. Phantom
11. You Only Love
12. Ballons
13. You're My Miracle (Japanese Version)

I bought this CD about a year and a half ago at the old Mitsuwa Marketplace in Torrance, thought I'd share it since I have all this music lying around on my computer.  

I have an extensive Asian Music Collection of a variety of South Korean, Japanese, and Chinese artists, so feel free to request an album or single!
